{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"54edccf8d7","title":"对陈正人关于社教蹲点情况报告的几条批注","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b85678bb06","index":0,"year":1965,"month":1,"day":15,"articleId":"54edccf8d7","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"干部和干部政策","id":"3df4ae75e1","type":"主题"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"指导理论","id":"c1c0033e04","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33f144c738","type":"title","text":"对陈正人关于社教蹲点情况报告的几条批注","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"54edccf8d7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82e801734a","type":"paragraph","text":"对陈正人关于社教蹲点情况报告的几条批注","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"54edccf8d7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2996242e1f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"54edccf8d7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"533905b217","type":"paragraph","text":"1965.01.15","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"54edccf8d7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"faa95adaec","type":"paragraph","text":"一、我也同意这种意见。官僚主义者阶级与工人阶级和贫下中农是两个尖锐对立的阶级。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"54edccf8d7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ddab10208f","type":"paragraph","text":"二、为什么不可以劳动四个到五个下午呢？剩下还有两个整天和四个到五个上午做别的事。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"54edccf8d7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82b03c6418","type":"paragraph","text":"三、管理也是社教。如果管理人员不到车间、小组搞“三同”，拜老师学一门至几门手艺，那就一辈子会同工人阶级处于尖锐的阶级斗争状态中，最后必然要被工人阶级把他们当作资产阶级打倒。不学会技术，长期当外行，管理也搞不好。以其昏昏，使人昭昭，是不行的。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"54edccf8d7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69e066660c","type":"paragraph","text":"四、这些人是已经变成或者正在变成吸工人血的资产阶级分子，他们怎么会认识足呢？这些人是斗争对象，革命对象，社教运动绝对不能依靠他们。我们能依靠的，只有那些同（工）人没有仇恨，而又有革命精神的干部。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"54edccf8d7","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}